Andhra Pradesh government also want to make the state Open Defecation Free by March 2018 for which it will construct about 22 Lakh toilets across the state till then. The government also want to provide all the facilities to the villages such as electricity, roads, gas and others before 2019 elections.
The CM urged the residents of the state to make Swachha Andhra Mission successful by taking a pledge to spare time for maintaining cleanliness in their respective areas.


